WEBVTT

00:03:30.282 --> 00:03:32.155
ninaweza kwenda nae pia.

00:03:32.976 --> 00:03:34.301
Hivyo nikashikilia

00:03:34.802 --> 00:03:36.468
na nikafunga macho

00:03:37.070 --> 00:03:38.220
kusikiliza,

00:03:38.678 --> 00:03:39.828
kusubiri.

00:03:40.314 --> 00:03:41.838
Na maombi yakawa na kelele.

00:03:42.428 --> 00:03:44.869
Na kelele za kujibu
wito wa maombi

00:03:44.893 --> 00:03:46.296
yakaenda juu zaidi.

00:03:46.725 --> 00:03:49.126
Na kinanda kikaunga
kuongezea wimbo.

00:03:49.150 --> 00:03:51.343
Na joto likaja juu kuongezea kwenye jasho.

00:03:51.660 --> 00:03:52.976
Na nikakaza mkono zaidi,

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:55.013
ili nisiwe wakuachwa
kwenye shamba.

00:03:55.037 --> 00:03:56.236
Macho yakabana zaidi

00:03:56.260 --> 00:03:59.232
ili nisione ngano ikitengwa
na makapi.

00:03:59.256 --> 00:04:01.625
Na sauti ikaita kutoka juu yetu: